Marianna City Farmers Market

The Marianna City Farmers Market is a family friendly market where farmers sell locally grown fresh fruits and vegetables at reasonable, low prices. They also have a nice selection of plants and flowers. Come shop where you have the opportunity to speak directly to the grower, and support our local farm businesses.

Products: All types of fresh vegetables, fruits, honey, flowers and plants.

Location: 2844 Madison Street, Marianna FL 32448.

Season: April-October

Hours: Saturdayâ€™s 7 AM-noon May-July; 8-Noon August-April
